Name: Button
Type: Demo
Fav: 1

ShortDescription: 
<
Click on the button to toggle it on or off. 
Anyone else viewing will see the change of state as well.
>

LongDescription:
<
This is a proof of concept of AJAX.
It's a really simple system with a button that is either
on or off.
Anyone currently on the page gets kept up to date with
the button's status.
Anyone currently on the page can change the state of
the button by clicking on it.
>
